ns0:svg.ns0:text: Look carefully at the picture showing elements of the weather. Identify the different parts and think about what they represent. Read the questions below and answer them based on what you see in the image.
1. What are the main things you see in this picture related to the weather?
2. Can you point out and name the different elements of the weather shown in the illustration?
3. What do you think the picture is trying to tell us about the weather?
4. How do the elements shown in the picture affect our daily lives or activities?
5. Imagine you are a weather reporter. Use the elements shown in the picture to create a short weather forecast for today.
